Subject: [PATCH 2/2] scsi/pcmcia/nsp_cs.c: Handle scsi_add_host failure
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
